This work is derived from Meccano's MeccaBrain open source library at:
  http://www.meccano.com/meccanoid-opensource

The library has been reworked to get rid of the features not supported by the Meccano M.A.X. It has also been enhanced to support most of the features of the Meccano M.A.X.

The open source licence for Meccano's meccanoid open source Arduino library has not been specified. As this is a derived work, the same license applies.

